research/*.log


# local operator credentials (never commit)
/_space_write_token_*.txt

# internal notes: audit reports, session handoffs, agent scratch.
# Three layers keep these out of anything published:
#   1. here — they cannot enter the git index by accident;
#   2. scripts/check_repo_hygiene.py — CI fails if one is tracked anyway;
#   3. scripts/deploy_hf.py — the HF Space upload publishes only git-tracked files,
#      because it reads the working tree and the Space is public.
/audit_*.md
/actual_plan.md
/_*.md
/.claude/
/.cx_polls/

# local research / handoff / assessment notes (root-level, never published;
# policy decided 2026-07-09). Standalone public candidates such as
# app/frontend/public/help.html, docs/data-flow.html, presentation.html and
# docs/plans history stay visible in `git status` until a product decision.
